Link: http://code.google.com/p/pycurves/
Author: Richard Tew <richard.m.tew@gmail.com>

Description
-----------

There are currently two scripts:

  static.py: Visualise a curve using different methods of interpolation.
  dynamic.py: Scroll along a curve using different methods of interpolation.

Supported curve types:

  - Linear.
  - Smooth step.
  - Hermite.

Dependencies
------------

Pyglet

Testing
-------

It was written using Python 2.6 on Windows and has not been tested on other
platforms.
